Modules and Packages

Modules: Collections of classes(variables+methods) , functions.
1. How to create a module - ex: calculator
2. how to call from one module to another. - Ex: calling calculator from operations

Ex with functions and classes
functions: EX: animal , bird and animalandbird files
classes: EX: a, b, ab files

two approach:
1. import from module name
2. from modulename import functions and classes

Pacakages: Collection of modules

EX 1
*pack1 =====> module 1 -----> display()  <<<<<<<<< client need access
       =====> module 2 -----> show()

EX 2
*package 1 ======> module 1 -------> display()  <<<<<<<<< customer need access
*package 1 ====> pack 2 ======> module 2 ------> show()

EX 3
*pack A ===> emp module ===> employee class ---> dispemp() method
*pack B ===> stu module ======> student class ---> dispstu() method
*pack C ===> principal












